physical_examinations.relevant_findings: Gen NAD, quite pleasant. Abdomen soft, appropriately tender, wounds clean, dry, intact. Cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm, no murmurs, rubs, or gallops. Lungs: Clear to auscultation. Extremities: Warm, without edema. Skin: No rash, anicteric. Genitourinary: No foley. Eyes: Extraocular movements intact. Head, ears, nose, throat: Mucous membranes moist, oropharynx clear. Neurological: Non-focal, follows commands, moves all extremities, wiggles toes; some generalized weakness. Psychiatric: Slow to answer questions, alert and oriented to 2.
